From 
@TheAthleticFC
: "In this story, I am not neutral and will not pretend to be," writes Adam Crafton. "Here is a gay guy’s account of the past month, reporting the World Cup in Qatar." https://nyti.ms/3PJFORy

“In my Indian American family, where no occasion passes without celebration, getting into the Christmas spirit means grooving to Bollywood music,” writes 
@SheilaYM
