@TheAthletic
: Trevor Lawrence’s dramatic ascent has propelled the Jaguars to the doorstep of the playoffs and begun to validate years of hype surrounding him. His alignment with first-year head coach Doug Pederson has been a significant catalyst. https://nyti.ms/3vqCTng

